 {
  "text": "Hello, Anna. I am the buyer from the Sao Paulo company. I want to talk about the price. Your sugar is very good, but the price is a little high for us. If we buy more, can you give a discount? We want a good deal for both companies. Please send me your best offer. Thank you.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a17_listening1.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Today I had my first negotiation. The buyer wanted a lower price. I said, if you buy fifty tons, I can give a small discount. He was happy with the offer. We talked about the terms and the delivery. In the end, we made a good deal and we signed the agreement. I am a real negotiator now.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a17_listening2.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "First, the buyer says the price is high. Then Anna makes an offer. Next, she says, if you buy more, I can give a discount. After that, they talk about the terms. Finally, they accept the deal and sign the agreement.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "pc17_order_deal.mp3"
 },
